<HEAD>Nine Biotech Products Used For Therapy, Vaccines</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Biotech Drugs</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the nine drugs and vaccines that have been approved for
human use by the Food and Drug Administration, according to a
survey by the Pharmaceutical Manufacturers Association. Listings
include the product name, the developer, and the health problem it
treats.
